o pays the IELTS exam fee?","a":"In India, the student pays IDP IELTS India on ieltsidpindia.com. FLC course fee is separate."},{"q":"Can we guarantee band 7?","a":"No. We set targets from diagnostic data and track mocks — outcomes depend on student effort and attendance."},{"q":"How many mock tests?","a":"Minimum four full mocks under exam conditions; more if below target before booking."},{"q":"Retake if score is low?","a":"Booster or skill-specific sessions based on weakest band; new enrollment as per fee policy."}],"compliance":["Never guarantee an IELTS band score","Separate coaching fee from exam registration fee","Signed enrollment agreement before batch start","Record diagnostic and mock scores on client file"],"proTips":["Set target band in writing at enrollment","Review mock trends weekly — not just overall average","Confirm Academic module for every study-abroad lead","Book exam only after two mocks within 0.5 of target"],"postApproval":["Collect official TRF when released","Update client record for admissions / visa team","Celebrate success or plan retake with gap analysis"],"performance":{"ourRate":82,"industryRate":68,"stats":[{"label":"Enrollments this year","value":"214"},{"label":"Hit target band","value":"176"},{"label":"Retake / booster","value":"38"}]},"approvalFactors":[{"label":"Attendance 80%+","ours":88,"benchmark":72},{"label":"Mock completion","ours":91,"benchmark":75},{"label":"Exam-ready booking","ours":85,"benchmark":70}],"timeline":[{"weeks":"1","title":"Diagnostic, enrollment, batch & books"},{"weeks":"2–7","title":"Classes, homework, skill drills, speaking mocks"},{"weeks":"6–8","title":"Full mock tests & exam readiness review"},{"weeks":"8–10","title":"Exam booking, test day prep, score follow-up"}],"relatedServices":[{"label":"IELTS — Test reference (official test guide)","libraryId":"b2000001-0001-4000-8000-000000000071"},{"label":"IELTS Academic Crash Course","libraryId":"b2000001-0001-4000-8000-000000000073"},{"label":"IELTS General Regular (with books)","libraryId":"b2000001-0001-4000-8000-000000000074"},{"label":"PTE Academic Regular","libraryId":""}],"changelog":[{"version":"v1.0","date":"June 2026","author":"Service Library","summary":"Initial IELTS Academic Regular coaching specimen."}],"staffNotes":[{"author":"Coaching team","date":"June 2026","text":"Do not move GT inquiries into Academic Regular — offer GT program or refer."}],"resources":[{"title":"IELTS test reference (FLC specimen)","url":"/specimens/coaching/ielts-test-reference.html","description":"Full test guide — acceptance matrix, test day, module samples"},{"title":"IELTS — Official site","url":"https://www.ielts.org/","description":"Academic vs GT, test format"},{"title":"IDP IELTS India — Book test","url":"https://www.ieltsidpindia.com/","description":"Sole booking channel in India"},{"title":"British Council India — IELTS prep","url":"https://www.britishcouncil.in/exam/ielts/faqs","description":"Prep only — BC does not deliver IELTS tests in India"}],"donts":{"dos":["Run diagnostic before quoting timeline","Track attendance and mocks","Confirm Academic module","Keep exam fee separate on invoice"],"donts":["Guarantee a band score","Book exam before readiness","Mix GT and Academic in same batch narrative","Skip enrollment agreement"],"mistakes":["Target 7 from diagnostic 5 in 4 weeks","No mock before exam date","Books not logged","Visa team not updated when target met"]},"sampleDocs":[{"title":"Sample diagnostic score sheet (mock)","description":"L/R/W/S breakdown template for intake.","docKind":"assessment","mimeType":"application/pdf"},{"title":"Sample 4-week study plan (mock)","description":"Skill rotation for Academic Writing Task 2.","docKind":"study_plan","mimeType":"application/pdf"},{"title":"Sample mock test feedback form (mock)","description":"Trainer band-style comments per section.","docKind":"feedback","mimeType":"application/pdf"}],"quiz":[{"question":"IELTS Academic is required for:","options":["Most univer